org.colomoto.biolqm.modifier

Interface ModelModifierService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractModelModifierService, ModelBooleanizerService, ModelReductionService, ModelReverserService, PerturbationService, SubSpaceService

    public interface ModelModifierService
extends Service
    A service providing modifiers for logical models. Such services should be registered for service discovery. To provide a generic interface, the services can construct new modifiers by parsing a String (provided by the user on the command-line or in a script). Implementors can provide additional methods with specialised API to setup the modifiers.
    Author:
    Aurelien Naldi
